#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_addresses
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_addresses`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_addresses` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `company_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `line1` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `line2` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `city` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `postal_code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `state` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `country` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `company_id` (`company_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_addresses` (`id`, `company_id`, `line1`, `line2`, `city`, `postal_code`, `state`, `country`, `phone`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('1', '45', '160 ITWARI ', 'itwari road', '45567', '', '1234', 'India', '56789045677778888999', '2019-12-15 13:47:04');
INSERT INTO `sma_addresses` (`id`, `company_id`, `line1`, `line2`, `city`, `postal_code`, `state`, `country`, `phone`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('2', '45', 'mahal', '', '09876', 'dfzsfdg', '4556777', '234567778', 'sdzfdgdfhfgh', '2019-12-15 13:50:20');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_adjustment_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_adjustment_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_adjustment_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `adjustment_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `adjustment_id` (`adjustment_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_adjustments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_adjustments`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_adjustments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `count_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_apinotify
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_apinotify`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_apinotify` (
  `id` int(100) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `merchant_code` bigint(100) NOT NULL,
  `customer_code` bigint(100) NOT NULL,
  `customer_name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `status` enum('pending','accepted','declined','onhold') NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_backup_database
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_backup_database`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_backup_database` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` longtext,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_brands
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_brands`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_brands` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `image` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `name` (`name`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=11 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_calendar
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_calendar`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_calendar` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `start` datetime NOT NULL,
  `end` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `color` varchar(7) NOT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_calendar` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `start`, `end`, `color`, `user_id`) VALUES ('3', 'ibm', 'good', '2016-11-21 00:00:00', '2016-11-22 00:00:00', '#3a87ad', '2');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_captcha
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_captcha`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_captcha` (
  `captcha_id` bigint(13) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `captcha_time` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `ip_address` varchar(16) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `word` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`captcha_id`),
  KEY `word` (`word`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_categories
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_categories`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_categories` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `image` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_category` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Category',
  `up_description` text COMMENT 'Category Description Uisng Urbanpiper',
  `up_enabled` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0 & null : disable, 1 enable',
  `up_add_status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=24 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_ccavenue
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_ccavenue`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_ccavenue` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `order_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `request_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `response_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `created_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  `update_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_combo_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_combo_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_combo_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_code` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(12,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=15 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_companies
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_companies`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_companies` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `group_id` int(10) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_name` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `customer_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_group_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `company` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vat_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pan_card` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `city` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `state` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `state_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `postal_code` varchar(8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `country` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pass_key` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_footer` text,
  `payment_term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `logo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `award_points` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `deposit_amount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price_group_name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `password` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `anniversary` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob_father` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob_mother` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob_child1` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob_child2` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_synced` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lat` float(10,6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lng` float(10,6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gstn_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email_verification_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `mobile_verification_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email_is_verified` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `mobile_is_verified` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `up_is_guest_mode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Data',
  `up_landmark` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Data',
  `up_sub_locality` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Data',
  `up_tag` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Data',
  `offline_reff_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `group_id` (`group_id`),
  KEY `group_id_2` (`group_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=60 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_contact_group
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_contact_group`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_contact_group` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `group_name` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `group_desc` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `group_created` datetime NOT NULL,
  `group_updated` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_contact_template
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_contact_template`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_contact_template` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `template_name` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `template_type` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '1=sms,2=email,3=push_message',
  `is_default` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `template_content` longtext NOT NULL,
  `template_created` datetime NOT NULL,
  `template_updated` datetime NOT NULL,
  `event_type` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '1=Bday,2=anniversary',
  `admin_note` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_costing
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_costing`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_costing` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_id` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_code` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `inventory` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `overselling` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=461 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_cron_user
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_cron_user`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_cron_user` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `postdate` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_currencies
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_currencies`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_currencies` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(5) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `rate` decimal(12,4) NOT NULL,
  `auto_update` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_currencies` (`id`, `code`, `name`, `rate`, `auto_update`) VALUES ('2', 'INR', 'Rupee', '1.0000', '0');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_custemail
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_custemail`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_custemail` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sender` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `subject` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `message` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `send_date` date NOT NULL,
  `customer_list` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_customer_groups
#

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_deleted_data
#

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deleted_related_data` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_deliveries
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_deliveries`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_deliveries` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `do_reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `sale_reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `address` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_type` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'partial / overall',
  `attachment` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivered_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_deliveries` (`id`, `date`, `sale_id`, `order_id`, `do_reference_no`, `sale_reference_no`, `customer`, `address`, `note`, `status`, `delivery_type`, `attachment`, `delivered_by`, `received_by`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('1', '2019-12-08 00:15:00', '140', NULL, 'DO/2019/12/0001', 'SALE/POS/2019/11/0111', 'mysimplisafe', '<p>H3B Nishat Enclave, 74 Bungalow Bhopal  462003 India<br>Tel: 7552555950 Email: info@simplypos.in</p>', '&lt;p&gt;product delivery date is near&lt;&sol;p&gt;', 'packing', 'overall', NULL, '', '', '1', NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `sma_deliveries` (`id`, `date`, `sale_id`, `order_id`, `do_reference_no`, `sale_reference_no`, `customer`, `address`, `note`, `status`, `delivery_type`, `attachment`, `delivered_by`, `received_by`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('2', '2019-12-06 00:32:00', '164', NULL, 'DO/2019/12/0002', 'SALE/POS/2019/12/0117', 'mysimplisafe', '<p>H3B Nishat Enclave, 74 Bungalow Bhopal  462003 India<br>Tel: 7552555950 Email: info@simplypos.in</p>', '', 'packing', 'overall', NULL, '', '', '1', NULL, NULL);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_deposits
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_deposits`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_deposits` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `company_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_division
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_division`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_division` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `code` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_eshop_authtoken
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_eshop_authtoken`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_eshop_authtoken` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `token` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `start_date` datetime NOT NULL,
  `end_date` datetime NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `user_id` (`user_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_eshop_order
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_eshop_order`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_eshop_order` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `is_cod` varchar(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_method_name` varchar(150) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `billing_name` varchar(155) DEFAULT NULL,
  `billing_addr` text,
  `billing_email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `billing_phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_name` varchar(150) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_addr` text,
  `shipping_email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_eshop_pages
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_eshop_pages`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_eshop_pages` (
  `id` tinyint(1) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `about_us` longtext NOT NULL,
  `contact_us` text NOT NULL,
  `terms` longtext NOT NULL,
  `p_policy` longtext NOT NULL,
  `faq` longtext NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_eshop_password_token
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_eshop_password_token`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_eshop_password_token` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `token` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `token_start` datetime NOT NULL,
  `token_end` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_eshop_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_eshop_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_eshop_settings` (
  `id` tinyint(1) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `banner_image_1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `banner_image_2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `banner_image_3` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_3` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `facebook_link` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `google_link` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `twitter_link` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shop_name` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shop_phone` varchar(35) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shop_email` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eshop_logo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `display_top_products` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '8',
  `default_banner` varchar(255) DEFAULT '{"1":"banner_1.jpg","2":"banner_2.jpg","3":"banner_3.jpg"}',
  `display_hot_offers` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `hot_offers_banner` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_text_1` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_text_1_2` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_text_2` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `homepage_image_text_3` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `show_homepage_images_text` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

  `billing_phone` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `billing_email` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `billing_addr1` text NOT NULL,
  `billing_addr2` text NOT NULL,
  `billing_city` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `billing_state` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `billing_country` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `billing_zipcode` varchar(7) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_name` varchar(150) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_phone` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_email` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_addr1` text NOT NULL,
  `shipping_addr2` text NOT NULL,
  `shipping_city` varchar(125) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_state` varchar(125) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_country` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `shipping_zipcode` varchar(7) NOT NULL,
  `user_photo` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `user_photo_path` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `user_id` (`user_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_login_attempts
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_login_attempts`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_login_attempts` (
  `id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `ip_address` varbinary(16) NOT NULL,
  `login` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `time` int(11) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=13 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_migrations
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_migrations`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_migrations` (
  `version` bigint(20) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_notifications
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_notifications`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_notifications` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `comment` text NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `from_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `till_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `scope` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '3',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_offers
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_offers`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_offers` (
  `id` bigint(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT 'offer_id',
  `offer_category_id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `offer_keyword` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_invoice_descriptions` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Display on Invoice',
  `offer_start_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_end_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_start_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_end_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_days` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_customer_group` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_warehouses` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_products` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_items_condition` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '1: Each Items, 2:Minimum 2 Items,..So on',
  `offer_on_products_quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_products_amount` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Without Tax',
  `offer_on_category` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_category_quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_category_amount` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Without Tax',
  `offer_on_brands` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_on_invoice_amount` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Without Tax',
  `offer_free_products` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_free_products_quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_discount_rate` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '10% OR 10',
  `offer_amount_including_tax` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0: Without Tax, 1: Including Tax',
  `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `is_delete` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_offers_categories
#

  `id` int(1) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT 'offer_category_id',

  `offer_category` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `is_delete` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_order_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_order_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_order_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL COMMENT 'order_id',
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `article_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Product Article Code',
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'real_unit_price - unit_discount - unit_tax',
  `unit_discount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Per Unit Discount',
  `unit_tax` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Per Unit Tax',
  `invoice_unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'real_unit_price - unit_discount - unit_tax',
  `invoice_net_unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'invoice_unit_price + unit_discount + unit_tax',
  `unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'net_unit_price + unit_tax',
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'mrp X quantity',
  `invoice_total_net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'invoice_net_unit_price X quantity',
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(unit_tax X quantity)',
  `tax_method` char(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0:Inclusive, 1:Exclusive',
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'tax_id',
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Tax Rate',
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'discount rate (% / Rs)',
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '( unit_discount X quantity )',
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Price Including Tax(unit_price X quantity)',
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Product Price',
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `mrp` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'For GST',
  `note` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_status` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'pending / partial / overall',
  `pending_quantity` decimal(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivered_quantity` decimal(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `gst_rate` decimal(6,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(%)',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_order_items` (`id`, `sale_id`, `product_id`, `product_code`, `article_code`, `product_name`, `product_type`, `option_id`, `net_unit_price`, `unit_discount`, `unit_tax`, `invoice_unit_price`, `invoice_net_unit_price`, `unit_price`, `quantity`, `net_price`, `invoice_total_net_unit_price`, `warehouse_id`, `item_tax`, `tax_method`, `tax_rate_id`, `tax`, `discount`, `item_discount`, `subtotal`, `serial_no`, `real_unit_price`, `sale_item_id`, `product_unit_id`, `product_unit_code`, `unit_quantity`, `cf1`, `cf2`, `cf3`, `cf4`, `cf5`, `cf6`, `cf1_name`, `cf2_name`, `cf3_name`, `cf4_name`, `cf5_name`, `cf6_name`, `mrp`, `hsn_code`, `note`, `delivery_status`, `pending_quantity`, `delivered_quantity`, `updated_at`, `gst_rate`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`) VALUES ('1', '1', '71', '85510932', '', 'Samosa', 'standard', '0', '60.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000', '60.0000', '60.0000', '60.0000', '4.0000', '60.0000', '60.0000', '2', '0.0000', '0', '1', '0.0000%', '0', '0.0000', '60.0000', '', '60.0000', NULL, '8', 'plate', '1.0000', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '15.0000', '', NULL, 'pending', '1.00', '0.00', '2020-02-10 20:25:08', '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_order_ref
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_order_ref`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_order_ref` (
  `ref_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `so` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `qu` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `po` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `to` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `pos` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `do` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `pay` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `re` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `rep` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `ex` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `ppay` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `qa` int(11) DEFAULT '1',
  `offapp` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Offline App',
  `eshop` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Eshop',
  `up` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `ordr` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Order',
  `re_ordr` int(11) DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Return Order',
  PRIMARY KEY (`ref_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_order_ref` (`ref_id`, `date`, `so`, `qu`, `po`, `to`, `pos`, `do`, `pay`, `re`, `rep`, `ex`, `ppay`, `qa`, `offapp`, `eshop`, `up`, `ordr`, `re_ordr`) VALUES ('1', '2017-01-01', '102', '16', '105', '78', '204', '3', '242', '40', '1', '5', '1', '7', '1', '1', '1', '18', '8');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_orders
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_orders`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_orders` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `invoice_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Order No. / Challan No.',
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `seller_id` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `seller` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Sub Total (Amount Without Tax )',
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000' COMMENT 'Product Discount + Order Discount',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000' COMMENT 'Product Tax+ Order Tax',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(Subtotal + Tax Total)',
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Order / Challan Status',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `total_items` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Is POS Sales',
  `paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'order_id',
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(12,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `cf1` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Patient name pharma',
  `cf2` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Doctor name pharma',
  `delivery_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending' COMMENT 'pending / partial / overall',
  `offer_category` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `kot_tokan` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_as_chalan` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `sale_invoice_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_orders` (`id`, `invoice_no`, `date`, `reference_no`, `customer_id`, `customer`, `biller_id`, `biller`, `seller_id`, `seller`, `warehouse_id`, `note`, `staff_note`, `total`, `product_discount`, `order_discount_id`, `total_discount`, `order_discount`, `product_tax`, `order_tax_id`, `order_tax`, `total_tax`, `shipping`, `grand_total`, `sale_status`, `payment_status`, `payment_term`, `due_date`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`, `total_items`, `pos`, `paid`, `return_id`, `surcharge`, `attachment`, `return_sale_ref`, `sale_id`, `return_sale_total`, `rounding`, `cf1`, `cf2`, `delivery_status`, `offer_category`, `offer_description`, `kot_tokan`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`, `sale_as_chalan`, `sale_invoice_no`) VALUES ('1', '19-20/00001\n', '2020-02-10 20:24:00', '2020/02/0014', '1', 'Walk-in Customer', '3', 'Simplysafe Biller', NULL, NULL, '2', '', '', '60.0000', '0.0000', NULL, '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000', '1', '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000', '60.0000', 'completed', 'pending', '0', NULL, '1', NULL, '2020-02-10 20:25:08', '1', '0', '0.0000', NULL, '0.0000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.0000', '0.0000', NULL, NULL, 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000', '1', NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_payments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_payments`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_payments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `transaction_id` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `cheque_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_holder` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_month` varchar(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_year` varchar(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos_paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `pos_balance` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `approval_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=262 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_payments` (`id`, `date`, `sale_id`, `return_id`, `purchase_id`, `reference_no`, `transaction_id`, `order_id`, `paid_by`, `cheque_no`, `cc_no`, `cc_holder`, `cc_month`, `cc_year`, `cc_type`, `amount`, `currency`, `created_by`, `attachment`, `type`, `note`, `pos_paid`, `pos_balance`, `approval_code`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('1', '2019-10-23 00:41:31', '1', NULL, NULL, 'IPAY/2019/10/0001', '', NULL, 'cash', '', '', '', '', '', '', '210.0000', NULL, '1', NULL, 'received', '', '210.0000', '0.0000', NULL, '2019-10-22 15:11:31');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_paynear
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_paynear`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_paynear` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `order_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `request_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `response_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `secret_token` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `created_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  `update_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_paypal
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_paypal`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_paypal` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `active` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `account_email` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `paypal_currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USD',
  `fixed_charges` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2.0000',
  `extra_charges_my` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '3.9000',
  `extra_charges_other` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '4.4000',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_paypal` (`id`, `active`, `account_email`, `paypal_currency`, `fixed_charges`, `extra_charges_my`, `extra_charges_other`) VALUES ('1', '1', '', 'INR', '0.0000', '0.0000', '0.0000');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_payswiff
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_payswiff`;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `order_id` int(11) NOT NULL COMMENT 'sale_id',
  `request_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `response_data` longtext NOT NULL,
  `secret_token` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `created_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  `update_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_pos_register
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_pos_register`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_pos_register` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `cash_in_hand` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `total_cash` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cheques` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cc_slips` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cash_submitted` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cheques_submitted` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cc_slips_submitted` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `closed_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_opened_bills` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `closed_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_pos_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_pos_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_pos_settings` (
  `pos_id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `eshop_order_tax` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `cat_limit` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `pro_limit` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_category` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_customer` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_biller` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `display_time` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'yes',
  `cf_title1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_title2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_value1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_value2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receipt_printer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cash_drawer_codes` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `focus_add_item` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_manual_product` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_selection` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `toggle_category_slider` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `toggle_subcategory_slider` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cancel_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `print_items_list` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `finalize_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `today_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `open_hold_bills` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `close_register` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `submit_and_print` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `other` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `keyboard` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `pos_printers` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `java_applet` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `product_button_color` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'default',
  `tooltips` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `paypal_pro` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `stripe` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `rounding` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `char_per_line` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '42',
  `pin_code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'purchase_code',
  `envato_username` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'envato_username',
  `version` varchar(10) DEFAULT '3.0.2.22',
  `after_sale_page` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `item_order` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `authorize` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `toggle_brands_slider` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `instamojo` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ccavenue` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paytm` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paytm_opt` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Paytm payment option',
  `credit_card` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `debit_card` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `gift_card` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `neft` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `google_pay` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `swiggy` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `zomato` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ubereats` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `magicpin` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `complimentary` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paynear` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `payumoney` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `default_eshop_warehouse` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_eshop_pay` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `eshop_cod` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `pos_screen_products` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0=default category,1=favorite products',
  `pos_theme` text NOT NULL,
  `default_eshop_theame` varchar(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'T1' COMMENT 'Ex.: T1 / T2 ...Tn',
  `eshop_free_delivery_on_order` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_auto_sms` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Send Invoice SMS On Submit Sale',
  `offers_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0: Disable , 1:Enable',
  `active_offer_category` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'offers_keyword',
  `recent_pos_limit` int(1) DEFAULT '20',
  `display_token` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Display Token No.',
  `alert_qty_auto_email` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0: Do Not Send, 1: On Closed Registered, 2: On Logout',
  `daily_sale_auto_email` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0: Do Not Send, 1: On Closed Registered, 2: On Logout',
  `display_category` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'yes=1, no=0',
  `pos_amount` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Checkout Amount Auto Selectd',
  `display_seller` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`pos_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_product_prices
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_product_prices`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_product_prices` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `price_group_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `price_group_id` (`price_group_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_products`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `article_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` char(255) NOT NULL,
  `unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `alert_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '20.0000',
  `image` varchar(255) DEFAULT 'no_image.png',
  `category_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `subcategory_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `tax_rate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `track_quantity` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `details` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `barcode_symbology` varchar(55) DEFAULT 'code128',
  `file` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_details` text,
  `tax_method` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `type` varchar(55) DEFAULT 'standard',
  `supplier1` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier1price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `promotion` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `promo_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `end_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier1_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brand` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `mrp` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_featured` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `divisionid` int(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `up_items` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Item',
  `food_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `code` (`code`),
  KEY `category_id` (`category_id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`),
  KEY `id_2` (`id`),
  KEY `category_id_2` (`category_id`),
  KEY `unit` (`unit`),
  KEY `brand` (`brand`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=77 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_purchase_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_purchase_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_purchase_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `adjustment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_method` varchar(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0:Inclusive, 1:Exclusive',
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `batch_number` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst_rate` decimal(6,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(%)',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=435 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_purchase_items_tax
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_purchase_items_tax`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_purchase_items_tax` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `attr_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `attr_name` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `attr_per` float NOT NULL,
  `tax_amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=598 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_purchases
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_purchases`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_purchases` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` text NOT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_purchase_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_purchase_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(12,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=119 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_purchases` (`id`, `reference_no`, `date`, `supplier_id`, `supplier`, `warehouse_id`, `note`, `total`, `product_discount`, `order_discount_id`, `order_discount`, `total_discount`, `product_tax`, `order_tax_id`, `order_tax`, `total_tax`, `shipping`, `grand_total`, `paid`, `status`, `payment_status`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`, `attachment`, `payment_term`, `due_date`, `return_id`, `surcharge`, `return_purchase_ref`, `purchase_id`, `return_purchase_total`, `rounding`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`) VALUES ('1', 'PO/2019/10/0001', '2019-10-19 05:23:00', '6', 'TEST SUP N', '1', '', '4761.9050', '0.0000', NULL, '0.0000', '0.0000', '238.0950', '1', '0.0000', '238.0950', '0.0000', '5000.0000', '0.0000', 'received', 'pending', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0.0000', NULL, NULL, '0.0000', '0.0000', '119.0476', '119.0476', '0.0000');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_quote_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_quote_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_quote_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `quote_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `mrp` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst_rate` decimal(6,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(%)',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `quote_id` (`quote_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=41 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_quote_items` (`id`, `quote_id`, `product_id`, `product_code`, `product_name`, `product_type`, `option_id`, `net_unit_price`, `unit_price`, `quantity`, `warehouse_id`, `item_tax`, `tax_rate_id`, `tax`, `discount`, `item_discount`, `subtotal`, `serial_no`, `real_unit_price`, `product_unit_id`, `product_unit_code`, `unit_quantity`, `mrp`, `hsn_code`, `gst_rate`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`) VALUES ('1', '1', '7', 'inc', 'inclusive  taxProduct', 'standard', '0', '95.2381', '100.0000', '1.0000', '1', '4.7619', '15', '5.0000%', '100', '100.0000', '100.0000', NULL, '200.0000', '4', 'pc', '1.0000', '300.0000', '', '2.5000', '2.3810', '2.3810', '0.0000');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_quotes
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_quotes`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_quotes` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `note` longtext,
  `internal_note` longtext,
  `total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,

) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=24 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_rewardpoint_sync
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_rewardpoint_sync`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_rewardpoint_sync` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `posttime` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_sale_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_sale_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_sale_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `article_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Product Article Code',
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'real_unit_price - unit_discount - unit_tax',
  `unit_discount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Per Unit Discount',
  `unit_tax` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Per Unit Tax',
  `invoice_unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'real_unit_price - unit_discount - unit_tax',
  `invoice_net_unit_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'invoice_unit_price + unit_discount + unit_tax',
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'net_unit_price + unit_tax',
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'mrp X quantity',
  `invoice_total_net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'invoice_net_unit_price X quantity',
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(unit_tax X quantity)',
  `tax_method` char(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0:Inclusive, 1:Exclusive',
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'tax_id',
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Tax Rate',
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'discount rate (% / Rs)',
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '( unit_discount X quantity )',
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Price Including Tax(unit_price X quantity)',
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Product Price',
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `mrp` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'For GST',
  `note` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_status` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'pending / partial / overall',
  `pending_quantity` decimal(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivered_quantity` decimal(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offlinepos_sale_reff` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offlinepos_saleitem_reff` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_order_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper order item id ',
  `up_packaging_charge` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Packaging Charges',
  `urbanpiper` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Urbanpiper  Sales',
  `up_option_order_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper option order ids using ","',
  `up_option_title` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper option Titles Using ","',
  `up_option_price` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper total option price',
  `up_option_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Option merchant_id',
  `up_option_response` longtext COMMENT 'Urbanpiper option all Response in json format',
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `gst_rate` decimal(6,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(%)',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`)

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_sales
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_sales`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_sales` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `invoice_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `seller_id` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `seller` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Sub Total (Amount Without Tax )',
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000' COMMENT 'Product Discount + Order Discount',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000' COMMENT 'Product Tax+ Order Tax',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(Subtotal + Tax Total)',
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `total_items` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Is POS Sales',
  `paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(12,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `eshop_sale` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `offline_sale` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `offline_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offline_payment_id` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offline_transaction_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Patient name pharma',
  `cf2` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Doctor name pharma',
  `delivery_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending' COMMENT 'pending / partial / overall',
  `eshop_order_alert_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0:Yet Not Alert, 1: Alert Display, 2: View Order',
  `offlinepos_sale_reff` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_category` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offer_description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `kot_tokan` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_channel` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT ' zomato, foodpanda, swiggy, ubereats',
  `up_response` longtext COMMENT 'Order Response UrbanPiper JSON Forrmat',
  `up_status` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'Placed',
  `up_item_level_total_charges` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Packing Charges & Others',
  `up_order_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Order ID',
  `up_delivery_datetime` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_coupon` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_next_status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '1.Acknowledged, 2. Confirmed, 3 . Food Ready, 4. Dispatched, 5. Modified, 6. Completed, 7. Cancelled ',
  `up_prev_state` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'urbanpiper prev state',
  `up_state_timestamp` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'urbanpiper status timestamp',
  `up_message` text COMMENT 'urbanpiper status message',
  `up_status_response` text,
  `up_sales_notification` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0:Yet Not Alert, 1: Alert Display, 2: View Order',
  `up_sales` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Urbanpiper Sales',
  `up_order_level_total_charges` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Order Level Other Charges',
  `order_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Order No. / Challan No.',
  `cgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=385 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_sales_items_tax
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_sales_items_tax`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_sales_items_tax` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `attr_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `attr_name` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `attr_per` float NOT NULL,
  `tax_amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1449 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_sessions
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_sessions`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_sessions` (
  `id` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `ip_address` varchar(45) NOT NULL,
  `timestamp` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `data` blob NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `ci_sessions_timestamp` (`timestamp`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_settings` (
  `setting_id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `logo` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `logo2` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `site_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `pos_version` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `language` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `default_warehouse` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `accounting_method` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `default_currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL,
  `default_tax_rate` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `rows_per_page` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `version` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1.0',
  `default_tax_rate2` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `dateformat` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sales_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quote_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `returnp_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expense_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_addition` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `theme` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `product_serial` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `default_discount` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_discount` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `discount_method` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `tax1` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `tax2` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `overselling` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `restrict_user` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `restrict_calendar` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `timezone` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iwidth` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `iheight` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `twidth` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `theight` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `watermark` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reg_ver` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `allow_reg` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reg_notification` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `auto_reg` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `protocol` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'mail',
  `mailpath` varchar(55) DEFAULT '/usr/sbin/sendmail',
  `smtp_host` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `smtp_user` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `smtp_pass` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `smtp_port` varchar(10) DEFAULT '25',
  `smtp_crypto` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `corn` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_group` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_email` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `mmode` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `bc_fix` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `auto_detect_barcode` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `captcha` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `reference_format` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `racks` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `attributes` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_expiry` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `decimals` tinyint(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `qty_decimals` tinyint(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `decimals_sep` varchar(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '.',
  `thousands_sep` varchar(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT ',',
  `invoice_view` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `tax_classification_view` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `default_biller` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `envato_username` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rtl` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `each_spent` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ca_point` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `each_sale` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sa_point` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `update` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `sac` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `display_all_products` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `display_symbol` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `symbol` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `remove_expired` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `barcode_separator` varchar(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '_',
  `set_focus` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `price_group` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `barcode_img` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `ppayment_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'POP',
  `disable_editing` smallint(6) DEFAULT '90',
  `qa_prefix` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `update_cost` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos_type` varchar(15) NOT NULL,
  `default_printer` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `auto_acceptance` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `invoice_view_purchase` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `invoice_product_image` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `tax_classification_view__purchase` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `sales_image` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `quotation_image` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `purchase_image` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `sms_sender` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'SIMPLY',
  `api_privatekey` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Required POS Version 3.00 or Above',
  `api_access` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Required POS Version 3.00 or Above',
  `add_tax_in_cart_unit_price` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `add_discount_in_cart_unit_price` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `offlinepos_warehouse` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `offlinepos_biller` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `show_quotation_unit_price` varchar(30) DEFAULT 'net_unit_price',
  `show_sales_unit_price` varchar(30) DEFAULT 'net_unit_price',
  `show_purchase_unit_cost` varchar(30) DEFAULT 'unit_cost',
  `synch_reward_points` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `synch_customers` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `up_balance_order` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Urban Piper Order Balance',
  `up_order_received` int(11) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT 'Total Received Order',
  `up_store_limits` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'Max Stores Limit',
  `display_zero_sale_for_product_report` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `sales_order_discount` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_order_discount` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_external_platform` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `invoice_format` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'inv',
  `invoice_length` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '4',
  `financial_type` varchar(1) DEFAULT 'F',
  `order_receipt_label` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'Order',
  `sale_multiple_return_edit` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`setting_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_skrill
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_skrill`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_skrill` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `active` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `account_email` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `secret_word` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `skrill_currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'INR',
  `fixed_charges` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `extra_charges_my` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `extra_charges_other` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_stock_count_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_stock_count_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_stock_count_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `stock_count_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_variant` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_variant_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expected` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `counted` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `stock_count_id` (`stock_count_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_stock_counts
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_stock_counts`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_stock_counts` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `initial_file` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `final_file` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brands` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brand_names` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `categories` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `category_names` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `products` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rows` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `differences` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `matches` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `missing` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `finalized` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_suspended_bills
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_suspended_bills`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_suspended_bills` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `kot_tokan` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `count` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `table_id` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `invoice_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=31 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_suspended_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_suspended_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_suspended_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `suspend_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `article_code` varchar(60) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `mrp` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `net_price` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL COMMENT 'MRP x Qty.',
  `hsn_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `isdelivered` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `note` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_net_unit_price` decimal(19,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_total_net_unit_price` decimal(19,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_unit_price` decimal(19,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_method` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0:Inclusive, 1:Exclusive',
  `unit_discount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_tax` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=45 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_tax_attr
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_tax_attr`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_tax_attr` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_transfer_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_transfer_items`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_transfer_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `transfer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `request_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sent_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `transfer_id` (`transfer_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=106 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_transfers
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_transfers`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_transfers` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `transfer_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `from_warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `from_warehouse_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `from_warehouse_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_units
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_units`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_units` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `base_unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `operator` varchar(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_value` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `operation_value` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `base_unit` (`base_unit`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `sma_units` (`id`, `code`, `name`, `base_unit`, `operator`, `unit_value`, `operation_value`, `updated_at`) VALUES ('1', 'Pis', 'Pis', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-10-11 20:13:16');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_callback_log
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_callback_log`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_callback_log` (
  `id` bigint(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `callback_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `callback_data` text,
  `callback_time` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_logs
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_logs`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_logs` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `channel` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT ' zomato, foodpanda, swiggy, ubereats',
  `response_json` text,
  `log_type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_orderrider
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_orderrider`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_orderrider` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `up_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'Urbanpiper order id',
  `channel_name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'urbanpiper, zomato, foodpanda, swiggy,  ubereats',
  `channel_order_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'channel order id',
  `current_state` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'At store, assigned',
  `alt_phone` bigint(20) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'delivery person alt phone no',
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'delivery person name',
  `phone` bigint(20) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'delivery person  phone no',
  `comments` text,
  `order_status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'assigned, at-store, unassigned, re-assigned, out-for-delivery, delivered',
  `created` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_order_rider_response` longtext COMMENT 'Urbanpiper response order rider',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_package_logs
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_package_logs`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_package_logs` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `package_orders` int(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `balance_order` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_products`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `food_type_id` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `active_status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `plat_urbanpiper` text COMMENT 'UrbanPiper Tags',
  `plat_zomato` text COMMENT 'Zomato Tags',
  `plat_foodpanda` text COMMENT 'Foodpanda tags',
  `plat_swiggy` text COMMENT 'Swiggy Tags',
  `plat_ubereats` text COMMENT 'Ubereats Tags',
  `available` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `sold_at_store` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `recommended` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_products_platform
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_products_platform`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_products_platform` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `up_store_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `up_store_ref_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `active_status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `urbanpiper` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zomato` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `foodpanda` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `swiggy` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ubereats` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `available` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `sold_at_store` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `recommended` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `tag_urbanpiper` text,
  `tag_zomato` text,
  `tag_swiggy` text,
  `tag_foodpanda` text,
  `tag_ubereats` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_settings` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `api_key` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `urbanpiper` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zomato` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `foodpanda` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `swiggy` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ubereats` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_active` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `is_delete` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: sma_up_status
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `sma_up_status`;

CREATE TABLE `sma_up_status` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_active` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `is_delete` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
